---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageUrl = 'https://allcalcnow.com/privacy-policy';
const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy';
const pageDescription =
  'AllCalcNow privacy policy. We are committed to protecting your privacy. No personal data is collected or stored on AllCalcNow.';

const lastUpdated = '22 May 2026';

const schemas = [
  {
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
    itemListElement: [
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://allcalcnow.com/' },
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Privacy Policy', item: pageUrl },
    ],
  },
  {
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'WebPage',
    name: pageTitle,
    url: pageUrl,
    description: pageDescription,
    dateModified: '2026-05-22',
    publisher: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'AllCalcNow', url: 'https://allcalcnow.com' },
  },
];

const navLinkClass =
  'inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-accent transition-colors hover:text-accent/80 hover:underline';
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} canonicalPath="/privacy-policy" schemas={schemas}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <nav aria-label="Back to site">
      <a href="/" class={navLinkClass}>
        <span aria-hidden="true">←</span> Back to AllCalcNow
      </a>
    </nav>

    <header class="mt-8 border-b border-border pb-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
        <strong class="text-text">AllCalcNow</strong> ·
        <a href="https://allcalcnow.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">allcalcnow.com</a>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </header>

    <article class="policy-prose mt-10 space-y-10 text-muted">
      <section id="introduction" aria-labelledby="h-intro">
        <h2 id="h-intro" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          This Privacy Policy explains how <strong class="text-text">AllCalcNow</strong> (“we”, “us”) handles information
          when you use <a href="https://allcalcnow.com" class="font-semibold text-accent hover:underline">allcalcnow.com</a>
          and our free online calculators.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          AllCalcNow is committed to your privacy. We built this site so you can get answers quickly—without creating an
          account, without handing over personal details, and without wondering what happens to the numbers you type into
          a mortgage, tip, or BMI calculator.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="not-collected" aria-labelledby="h-not-collected">
        <h2 id="h-not-collected" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">2. What AllCalcNow Does NOT Collect</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 leading-relaxed">
          <li><strong class="text-text">No account or registration</strong> — you never need to sign up to use AllCalcNow.</li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">No calculation inputs or results stored</strong> — amounts, dates, weights, and other
            values you enter are processed in your browser. We do not save them on our servers.
          </li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">No sale of personal data</strong> — we do not sell your information to third parties.</li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Browser-only calculations</strong> — except where noted below (e.g. live exchange rates),
            the math runs locally on your device.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="automatic" aria-labelledby="h-automatic">
        <h2 id="h-automatic" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">3. What AllCalcNow May Collect Automatically</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          We may collect <strong class="text-text">anonymous page view data</strong> only—such as which pages were visited,
          approximate browser type, and device category (mobile or desktop). This data cannot reasonably be used to identify
          you personally.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          When enabled, this is done via <strong class="text-text">Google Analytics in anonymous mode</strong> (or equivalent
          privacy-oriented settings) to understand how people use AllCalcNow and to improve the site. IP addresses are not
          used to build individual profiles.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="cookies" aria-labelledby="h-cookies">
        <h2 id="h-cookies" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">4. Cookies Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">AllCalcNow uses a minimal approach to cookies:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 leading-relaxed">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Analytics cookies only</strong> — to measure anonymous traffic, if analytics is active.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">No advertising cookies</strong> — we do not run ad networks that track you across sites.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">No personal tracking cookies</strong> — no cross-site profiling for marketing.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          You can disable or delete cookies in your browser settings (Chrome, Safari, Firefox, Edge, and others all offer
          this under Privacy or Cookies). Blocking cookies may limit analytics but will not stop calculators from working.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="third-party" aria-labelledby="h-third-party">
        <h2 id="h-third-party" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">5. Third Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">AllCalcNow may connect to the following services:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 leading-relaxed">
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-border/80 bg-card px-4 py-3">
            <strong class="text-text">Google Analytics</strong> — anonymous traffic data only, to improve AllCalcNow.
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-border/80 bg-card px-4 py-3">
            <strong class="text-text">Exchange rate API</strong> (e.g. ExchangeRate-API) — fetches public currency rates.
            No personal data from you is sent; only a request for rate data.
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-border/80 bg-card px-4 py-3">
            <strong class="text-text">Google Fonts</strong> — delivers web fonts for readable typography. Standard font
            requests may include your IP address as part of normal web delivery; see Google’s policies for details.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          Each third party has its own privacy policy. We choose partners that align with a lightweight, privacy-respecting
          experience.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="children" aria-labelledby="h-children">
        <h2 id="h-children" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          AllCalcNow is safe for all ages. Our calculators are educational and practical tools. We do not knowingly collect
          personal data from children, and we do not require users to disclose their age. If you believe a child has submitted
          personal information through our contact form, please email us and we will delete it promptly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="changes" aria-labelledby="h-changes">
        <h2 id="h-changes" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">7. Policy Changes</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          AllCalcNow may update this Privacy Policy occasionally—for example, when we add a new calculator, change analytics
          providers, or adjust legal requirements. The “Last updated” date at the top of this page shows the current version.
          Please check back periodically for the latest wording.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" aria-labelledby="h-contact">
        <h2 id="h-contact" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          Questions about privacy at AllCalcNow? Contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <a href="mailto:privacy@allcalcnow.com" class="text-base font-semibold text-accent hover:underline">
            privacy@allcalcnow.com
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          For general enquiries, you may also use our <a href="/contact" class="font-semibold text-accent hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>

    <footer class="mt-14 border-t border-border pt-8">
      <nav aria-label="Back to site footer">
        <a href="/" class={navLinkClass}>
          <span aria-hidden="true">←</span> Back to AllCalcNow
        </a>
      </nav>
      <p class="mt-6 text-center text-xs text-muted">© {new Date().getFullYear()} AllCalcNow.com</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-prose a {
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
